SIMPLE: skater
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Skater
<hw>Skat"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One who
skates.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>Any one of numerous species of
hemipterous insects belonging to <gen>Gerris</gen>,
<gen>Pyrrhocoris</gen>, <gen>Prostemma</gen>, and allied genera. They
have long legs, and run rapidly over the surface of the water, as if
skating.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Skatol</ent>⟦br⟧
